ZH: 他不肯帮我。
EN: He refuses to help me.

ZH: 她不肯和我一起去看电影。
EN: She is unwilling to go to the movies with me.

ZH: 我不肯原谅他的错误。
EN: I won't forgive his mistake.

ZH: 他不肯接受我的道歉。
EN: He doesn't want to accept my apology.

ZH: 她不肯离开家人。
EN: She is unwilling to leave her family.

ZH: 我不肯相信他所说的话。
EN: I refuse to believe what he said.

ZH: 我不肯放弃我的梦想。
EN: I am unwilling to give up on my dreams.

ZH: 孩子不肯吃蔬菜。
EN: The child refuses to eat vegetables.

ZH: 我不肯屈服于困难。
EN: I refuse to give in to difficulties.

ZH: 他不肯付钱。
EN: He is unwilling to pay.

ZH: 她不肯离开他的身边。
EN: She refuses to leave his side.

ZH: 我不肯为别人改变自己。
EN: I am unwilling to change myself for others.

ZH: 他不肯听取我的建议。
EN: He is not willing to listen to my advice.

ZH: 我不肯去那个地方。
EN: I refuse to go to that place.

ZH: 他不肯道歉。
EN: He refuses to apologize.

ZH: 她不肯相信他的谎言。
EN: She is unwilling to believe his lies.

ZH: 我不肯把问题扔在一边。
EN: I won't ignore the problem.

ZH: 他不肯接受失败的事实。
EN: He doesn't want to accept the fact of failure.

ZH: 她不肯承认她错了。
EN: She refuses to admit she was wrong.

ZH: 我不肯和他合作。
EN: I am unwilling to cooperate with him.
